    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(S) In nomine domini nostri Iehsu Christi Dei eterni, anno ab incarnationis
                        eius millesimo centesimo quinquagesimo quinto, septimo idus ianuarii,
                        indictione quarta. Manifestus sum ego <persName ref="#people/3215"
                            >Passavanti</persName> quondam <persName ref="#people/3216"
                            >Sesmondini</persName> filius quia pro domini amore et anime mee
                        redemptione offero et inrevocabiliter trado omnipotenti deo et <rs
                            key="#Churches">ecclesie</rs>
                        <orgName ref="#juridical_persons/3206" key="#Churches #Hospitals">sanctorum
                            eius Iacobi et Gilii</orgName> et aliorum ad utilitatem et commodum <rs
                            key="#Hospitals">hospitalis</rs>
                        <placeName ref="#places/3207" key="#Churches #Hospitals"
                            >Altepascensis</placeName> unam integram petiam de terra que videtur
                        esse posita prope <rs key="#Castle">castellum</rs> quod nuncupatur
                            <placeName ref="#places/3210" key="#Castle #Roads">Puteum</placeName>,
                        in loco qui dicitur <placeName ref="#places/3210" key="#Wine"><rs
                                key="#Wine">Vignale</rs> Donicato</placeName>. Et est tenens unum
                        caput in <rs key="#Roads">via pubblica</rs>, aliud in terra <persName><name
                                ref="Hubertus">Uberti</name></persName> quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Iohannes">Iohannis</name></persName> et <persName><name
                                ref="Geca">Geche</name></persName> filie quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Lucterius">Loctieri</name></persName>. Latus unum tenet in
                        terra iamdicti Uberti, aliud in terra similiter Geche suprascripte.
                            <foreign>Pena</foreign> in duplum (…) et insuper penam argenti optimi
                        solidorum centum. Quia tali ordine hanc cartulam offertionis scribere rogavi
                            <persName key="#Writer #Notary #Tabellio"><name ref="Heinricus"
                                >Henrigum</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarium</rs> domni inperatoris. Actum in pede castri
                        Putensi, in domo et super fenestra <persName><name ref="Martinus"
                                >Martinelli</name></persName>. Signa manus suprascripti Passavanti,
                        qui alacri animo hanc offertionis cartulam scribere rogavit. Signa manus
                            <persName key="#Witness" ref="#people/3227">Ughiccione</persName>
                        quondam <persName ref="#people/3228">Benefatii</persName> atque <persName
                            key="#Witness" ref="#people/3229">Paltonieri</persName> et <persName
                            key="#Witness" ref="#people/3234">Buiamonti</persName> atque <persName
                            key="#Witness" ref="#people/3235">Bonefatii</persName> filiorum
                        suprascripti Ughiccionis rogatorum <rs key="#Witness">testium</rs>. (S) Ego
                        Henrigus domni imperatoris <rs key="#Tabellio">tabellio</rs> rogatu
                        Passavanti peractis et perfectis complevi et dedi.</ab>
                </div>
